Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大男生合夥來欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是差勁  差勁透了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊  遠坂  這跟你又沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們也來對我做同樣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不就和我有關係了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保持平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想操控魔力必須要時刻控制好自己的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果操控有誤  魔力會反噬自己的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過度的力量與錯誤的方法不僅對自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會給身邊的人帶來危害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻牢記正確的流程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是遠坂家的家訓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「時刻保持從容  優雅處事」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到這種事琴音可不能忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果錯在他們的話  你可得發發脾氣才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜真是厲害  敢那麼直接地說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有呢  這是很普通的事情吧  或者說理所當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這都是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  再多教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要怎麼才能做出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛  對於現在的凜來說或許有些難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  只要凜你每天努力  總有一天能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  你可是遠坂家的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小凜  這個地方可不可以教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個在教科書的23頁有寫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊只是在這裡計算錯誤了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題嘛…你看  和這個例題是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  凜好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來坐下  我按順序教你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要去禪城那邊住才行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦聖杯戰爭開始  冬木市就已不算安全之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想幫父親贏得聖杯戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  不能給爸爸添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是累贅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非如此  這次要以比過去更齊全的準備來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中也包含了確保你們的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此凜和媽媽最好還是離開冬木市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也能幫上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  只是父親還沒有教給我足夠的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我自己學就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完…完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.25,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟此門者為何許人也？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.07,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或可為吾友朋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.95,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,執吾之手  以此為誓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.58,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相會於吾陋室之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:38.90,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝之手   是小？是大？是瘦？是硬？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.25,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Du,  wer die Tür geöffnet hat
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.07,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wird  freunde  sein
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.95,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Für die Aussage nimm meine Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.58,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wir  werden  in  meinem  Zimmer  treffen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:38.90,bird,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sind deine Hände, Klein? Gross? Schlank? Steif?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把書合上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對凜來說  要看這本書還為時過早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上有些東西自身就帶有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫魔力針
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然平時不會有任何反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果附近有魔術的痕跡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜  你用魔力發動它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後對於剛才那本書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有這種反應的東西是凜還無法應付的  必須小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這個送給凜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算提前送你的生日禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等聖杯戰爭結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你嘗試一下更為正式的寶石魔術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於  異變開始產生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是自習哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上的新聞也是綁架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}最近冬木市經常發生兒童突然失蹤的案件…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師他們一直在開會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第五節課不上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但老師說得待在家裡不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是綁架案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.02,0:09:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被綁架的都是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體好像沒有放進棺材裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟樣子很淒慘啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件的確是在冬木市發生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和琴音同班的遠坂…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在電話無人接聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在聽到「嘀」的一聲後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…夜晚的冬木市？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和白天完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人感覺好不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒見過這樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是說到處都有魔力的痕跡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:10:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得找到琴音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這麼晚了還帶著孩子外出？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險  要是被發現了肯定會被送回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  要好好走路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩的數量變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要躲起來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去  什麼也做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被下了什麼魔術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎麼  迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們正準備開派對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人數還有點不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要也來幫幫忙呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這種事就得人多才熱鬧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑什麼跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是用那手鐲  把大家給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要破壞掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  你還是願意幫忙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性注入太多魔力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴音！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可沒時間哭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下估計要挨老爺罵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小凜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成功了啊  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有這種反應的東西是凜還無法應付的  必須小心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜…沒想到竟然會去了冬木市…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凜她沒事  只是睡著了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁夜君？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是間桐家的魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以肉體為巢穴  以靈魂為食糧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這些代價才能換來如此的魔道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小櫻會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她變成這樣之前  我一定會將她救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臓硯想要的只有聖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他答應我只要能得到那東西  他便會放了小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說…聖杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Servant是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會輸給任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於現在的小櫻來說  就連抱有希望也是一種折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  請你代替那孩子祈禱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也為了小櫻的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁夜君  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  我們能回到當初一起在這個公園嬉戲的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  小凜和小櫻也會重新成為姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  葵姐  你也不必再哭泣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁夜君  你是想死嗎？要和時臣同歸於盡？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綺禮大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放著遠坂時臣的夫人和千金不管  真的妥當嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續監視Berserker的Master
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.17,0:20:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是小事  但我也確實能做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要說這樣就能獨當一面吧  我卻又半途就暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我還不夠成熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  這也只是現在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有足夠的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天  我會以遠坂的魔術師這個身份開始戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這隨時可能到來的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要勤學苦練  謹記父親的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時只需要將自己所能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力又優雅地完成就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有慾望的王者連裝飾品都不如！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能保護弱者的話  又有什麼意義？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會有什麼損失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是固有結界？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本王要親手殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是想要征服世…哇！
